This means that you can do what you like to it or with it.  We used to
say that we placed it in the public domain, but it's not clear that
placing it voluntarily in the public domain has any legal force.  Feel
free to use it, modify it, sell it, change the license and otherwise
go wild, but we accept no responsibility for any of your actions, nor
for their consequences.

